1
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:15,700
Ye.

2
00:00:16,780 --> 00:00:18,140
Our parents died early.

3
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:21,260
You've suffered a lot with me growing up.

4
00:00:21,490 --> 00:00:23,870
Now that I have the means to send you abroad.

5
00:00:23,870 --> 00:00:25,450
I want to give you a new identity.

6
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:26,740
That way, I can feel more at ease.

7
00:00:26,740 --> 00:00:28,510
But I'll be all alone overseas,

8
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:30,510
with no one I know around me.

9
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:32,420
What if I miss you?

10
00:00:32,870 --> 00:00:34,160
I'll come visit you.

11
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,470
When that time comes,

12
00:00:37,230 --> 00:00:38,560
you can be my tour guide.

13
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:40,100
Then pinky swear with me.

14
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,280
Yi.

15
00:00:51,150 --> 00:00:52,830
Back then, to protect me,

16
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,370
you sent me away.

17
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:58,190
When we met again, you were already gone.

18
00:00:58,790 --> 00:01:00,830
I'll take over your vengeance

19
00:01:01,770 --> 00:01:03,630
.and everything you set out to do.

20
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:18,850
Miss.

21
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,870
Have you seen this person before?

22
00:01:20,870 --> 00:01:21,830
No.

23
00:01:23,630 --> 00:01:25,760
Why is my picture on the wanted poster?

24
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,510
Hello, who are you calling for?

25
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:29,220
Hello, is this the police?

26
00:01:29,220 --> 00:01:30,289
I'd like to report something.

27
00:01:30,289 --> 00:01:32,490
Second Young Madam of the Yin family...

28
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:51,030
[WANTED]

29
00:01:52,509 --> 00:01:53,509
Young lady.

30
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:56,750
Come out.

31
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,130
Boss, are you okay?

32
00:02:12,130 --> 00:02:13,130
Boss, are you alright?

33
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:13,920
I'm fine.

34
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,510
Go inform Young Master Huanyuan.

35
00:02:17,510 --> 00:02:18,829
that I've found

36
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:20,790
the person he's looking for.

37
00:02:20,950 --> 00:02:21,860
Young lady.

38
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,079
You can't run.

39
00:02:23,550 --> 00:02:24,380
Stop.

40
00:02:27,329 --> 00:02:28,930
If you run again, I'll shoot.

41
00:02:34,110 --> 00:02:35,320
If you don't stop,

42
00:02:35,730 --> 00:02:37,170
my next shot

43
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,320
won't just graze you.

44
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:28,750
[Your Sunshine]

45
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:30,960
[Episode 2: The Rabbit That Bites]

46
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:32,900
Boss! Boss!

47
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:41,230
The Thunder Gang people are here.

48
00:03:41,230 --> 00:03:42,510
Get the boss out first.

49
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:46,680
Protect her.

50
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,360
What are you waiting for?

51
00:04:49,550 --> 00:04:54,340
♪ How many people in this world
love across great divides ♪

52
00:04:54,360 --> 00:05:00,590
♪ Like waiting for migratory birds that
never return, trapped in eternal winter ♪

53
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,420
♪ That sea guards the mountains,
burning with every wave ♪

54
00:05:02,420 --> 00:05:04,820
The Lu family
can't escape what they owe us.

55
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,470
If you don't come out now,

56
00:05:06,470 --> 00:05:07,520
you'll regret it.

57
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:13,750
♪ Only then may fate show mercy ♪

58
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:19,940
♪ How strange, meeting
and parting, like accidents ♪

59
00:05:19,970 --> 00:05:26,070
♪ Like glimpsing light,
yet unable to hold it ♪

60
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:26,160
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

61
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,490
♪ Half my world is dust ♪

62
00:05:28,490 --> 00:05:29,280
Hide.

63
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:40,230
♪ But I was lucky to have
seen the purest white in you ♪

64
00:05:40,659 --> 00:05:45,590
♪ Must we always have
regret to be complete? ♪

65
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:48,770
♪ So mismatched we can't fit ♪

66
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:51,980
♪ Yet we still met—how cruel ♪

67
00:05:52,010 --> 00:05:55,570
♪ I tried to understand and become ♪

68
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:58,290
♪ The rose they all praise ♪

69
00:05:58,290 --> 00:05:59,090
Are you okay?

70
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:00,030
♪ But worldly tastes make people dull ♪

71
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:00,780
I'm fine.

72
00:06:00,970 --> 00:06:01,730
Zhuoqian.

73
00:06:02,210 --> 00:06:02,880
It's too loud.

74
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,530
Let's go.

75
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:07,840
♪ And courage comes from ignorance ♪

76
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:11,100
♪ Even if the wind never stops ♪

77
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:14,400
♪ I'll cross the boundary of pride ♪

78
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:17,570
♪ Follow across barren coordinates ♪

79
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:21,290
♪ The brilliance you
shone in that instant ♪

80
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:27,810
♪ Made me drop my guard and cry ♪

81
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:37,950
In that moment, I knew

82
00:06:39,420 --> 00:06:40,880
you're still the same you.

83
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:44,540
You haven't changed.

84
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:56,490
[The Next Day
Yin Zhuofeng's Private Residence]

85
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,720
You go.

86
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:27,310
She's probably still mad at me.

87
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:27,940
Alright.

88
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:39,400
Lu Ye, are you out of your mind?

89
00:07:39,590 --> 00:07:41,310
I just treated your wound yesterday,

90
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:43,159
and today you throw this thing at me?

91
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:43,930
What's wrong with you?

92
00:07:43,930 --> 00:07:45,730
Sorry. I didn't know it was you.

93
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:47,320
I hit the wrong person.

94
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,300
So just now, that was meant for me?

95
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,409
Can I go now?

96
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:15,230
You're this hungry

97
00:08:15,650 --> 00:08:18,310
and still had the strength
to throw things at me?

98
00:08:29,540 --> 00:08:30,340
After you eat,

99
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:32,140
I'll have someone take you away.

100
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,549
You can go back to school.

101
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,679
This money should be enough.

102
00:08:36,409 --> 00:08:38,070
My sister can't rest in peace.

103
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:40,200
I must find out the truth.

104
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:42,070
I'll take her vengeance

105
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,510
on myself.

106
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:50,310
Right now, you don't have
any means to take revenge.

107
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:53,180
And I'm not in the habit
of sending people to die.

108
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:54,640
Just listen to my brother.

109
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,220
With what you have now,

110
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,790
you can't even protect yourself,

111
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:58,500
let alone

112
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:00,770
take revenge.

113
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:03,540
Then tell me,

114
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:05,820
what does self-protection require?

115
00:09:06,770 --> 00:09:09,230
The ability
to protect yourself starts with

116
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,880
being able to defeat me.

117
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,090
Fine.

118
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:20,740
Yin Zhuofeng,

119
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:22,300
if I beat him,

120
00:09:23,310 --> 00:09:24,430
I'll decide

121
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:25,590
where I'll go.

122
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:26,890
Zhuoqian,

123
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,270
take her to the station.

124
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,540
Let's go.

125
00:09:50,330 --> 00:09:51,090
Get down!

126
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:03,830
Are you a dog?

127
00:10:04,590 --> 00:10:05,190
No,

128
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,290
I'm a rabbit.

129
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:07,880
Just wanted to show you

130
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:10,580
even you have moments
when you're caught off guard.

131
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:11,350
If I had

132
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,630
a knife just now,

133
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,370
you'd be worse off than bitten.

134
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:15,700
I have my own strengths.

135
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,240
Why can't I have a try?

136
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,170
Alright.

137
00:10:20,140 --> 00:10:21,340
Then go ahead and try.

138
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,720
If you can tear off

139
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,950
just one button from Zhuoqian's shirt,

140
00:10:26,090 --> 00:10:27,490
I'll count it as your win.

141
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:28,920
Zhuofeng,

142
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:31,220
am I really going to fight her?

143
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:33,740
She's a girl.

144
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:35,560
It doesn't feel right.

145
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:43,700
First,

146
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:46,230
my sister hired someone

147
00:10:46,230 --> 00:10:47,690
to teach me self-defense.

148
00:10:47,890 --> 00:10:48,650
Second,

149
00:10:49,110 --> 00:10:50,170
I'm older than you.

150
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,880
You should call me "Sister."

151
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:08,170
Don't fight me.

152
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,520
You can't win.

153
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:27,610
You can give up anytime.

154
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:32,300
It's not…

155
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,300
Over!

156
00:12:07,210 --> 00:12:08,050
Zhuofeng.

157
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,170
She lost.

158
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,310
I won.

159
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:22,470
That's enough.

160
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:31,970
Wait here.

161
00:12:41,730 --> 00:12:43,860
You're being hunted all over Hai City.

162
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:44,870
Listen to me,

163
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:46,180
leave.

164
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,960
When the time is right,

165
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:50,510
I'll give you answers

166
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,040
about your sister's death.

167
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,170
Yin Zhuofeng,

168
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,960
I choose the second path.

169
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,280
What second path?

170
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:12,970
I figured

171
00:13:14,010 --> 00:13:16,270
you wouldn't only give me one way forward.

172
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:16,980
Right?

173
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:18,990
You stick to your plan.

174
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:20,470
I'll stick to my belief.

175
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:21,930
If I'm not good enough,

176
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,990
then help me.

177
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,610
Let me create a miracle.

178
00:13:25,070 --> 00:13:26,730
Let me be the wind at your back.

179
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:33,350
You really think a lot.

180
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,160
You want to create a miracle?

181
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:46,980
Alright.

182
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:48,530
Right now, the sky's full of clouds.

183
00:13:48,530 --> 00:13:50,190
It's going to rain any second.

184
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,630
If you can make the clouds part

185
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,490
and stars appear in five minutes,

186
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:54,900
I'll agree.

187
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,630
Can I even control the clouds?

188
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,760
I want a miracle.

189
00:13:59,330 --> 00:13:59,970
Zhuoqian,

190
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:01,090
what time is it?

191
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:03,240
9:18.

192
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,000
Five-minute countdown,

193
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:08,090
starts now.

194
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,280
Yin Zhuofeng,

195
00:14:29,350 --> 00:14:30,420
watch closely.

196
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:32,600
I'll bring out the stars for you.

197
00:15:38,590 --> 00:15:39,900
It's now 9:22.

198
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,450
Time for the miracle.

199
00:15:49,610 --> 00:15:50,280
Get in.

200
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:13,820
[Hai City – Bronze Leaf]

201
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,590
What is this place?

202
00:16:17,140 --> 00:16:18,090
Bronze Leaf.

203
00:16:19,290 --> 00:16:20,080
Come on.

204
00:16:20,930 --> 00:16:21,780
Go in.

205
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,460
What's a woman
like you doing at Bronze Leaf?

206
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:44,860
This is what you've achieved so far?

207
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:46,210
The exit is over there.

208
00:16:46,610 --> 00:16:47,340
Choose for yourself.
